== 利用状况 ==
本站是浦西距离[[外灘|外灘]]最近的地铁车站，客流量长期高企，尤以访沪游客居多<ref>{{cite news|author=王建慧|url=http://news.sina.com.cn/c/2010-07-31/132617892665s.shtml|title=外滩导向牌导出“一头雾水”|publisher=[[新闻晚报|新闻晚报]]|date=2010-07-31|accessdate=2016-11-02|archive-date=2019-06-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190612034954/http://news.sina.com.cn/c/2010-07-31/132617892665s.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|author=陈轶珺|url=http://sh.eastday.com/m/20141030/u1ai8418133.html|title=地铁告示牌英语翻译闹笑话："到以下车站"翻成"到以下网站"|publisher=东方网|date=2014-10-30|accessdate=2016-11-02|archive-date=2017-01-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170105235515/http://sh.eastday.com/m/20141030/u1ai8418133.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，而在外滩举办重大活动时（如国庆）会采取临时封站措施，封站期间列车不停靠本站，不办理进出站业务。<ref>{{cite news|author=董巍|url=http://news.sohu.com/20040928/n222280915.shtml|title=彩灯开放夜地铁封两站|publisher=[[青年报|青年报]]|date=2004-09-28|accessdate=2016-11-02|archive-date=2017-01-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170106035420/http://news.sohu.com/20040928/n222280915.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|author=李继成|url=http://www.thepaper.cn/newsDetail_forward_1414292|title=上海跨年夜临时封闭离外滩最近地铁站，其他车站将视情况封闭|publisher=[[澎湃新闻|澎湃新闻]]|date=2015-12-28|accessdate=2016-11-02|archive-date=2019-06-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190612184725/http://www.thepaper.cn/newsDetail_forward_1414292|dead-url=no}}</ref>截至2010年，本站日均进出站客流已逾10万人次。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.163.com/10/0929/09/6HO6TMJ300014AED.html|title=因部分路段实行交通管制人民广场站或不按常规换乘|publisher=[[青年报|青年报]]|date=2010-09-29|accessdate=2016-11-02|archive-date=2019-01-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190119174743/http://news.163.com/10/0929/09/6HO6TMJ300014AED.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

